Description

New Delhi Government Jobs for 12th pass and diploma holders has been published by Delhi Subordinate Services Selection Board for the posts of Trained Graduate Teacher, Assistant Teacher (Primary, Nursery), Jr Secretarial Assistant, Counselor, Head Clerk, Patwari. If you are searching for a government job in Delhi then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these posts, from 25-05-2021, and till 04-07-2021. If you are interested in all these posts and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for other candidates is only Rs. 100/-.
  • No application fee for Women, SC, ST, PWD & Ex-Serviceman candidates

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 25-05-2021.
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 04-07-2021

How to apply for DSSSB Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Trained Graduate Teacher, Assistant Teacher (Primary, Nursery), Jr Secretarial Assistant, Counselor, Head Clerk, Patwari. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of DSSSB and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by DSSSB.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
